Sense includes compiled dictionary data from Rime “pinyin-simp”,
CC-CEDICT and chinese-idiom-chengyu, plus a popularity-ranked English word
list derived from popular-english-words. The application code remains under
the repository's MIT License. The generated Chinese dictionary and bigram
assets are separately distributed under CC BY-SA 4.0 because they incorporate
CC-CEDICT data. The imported idiom source remains available under its MIT
License and the English word-list asset remains under the ISC License.

