syllables outside Sense's pinned inventory, and writes
ime-service/src/main/lexicon/sense_idioms.dict.tsv (1,014,156 bytes; SHA-256
2175614fec07000bb1f5bdec45df10eea2e50580c4d50d7fc5931e91ec945007).

